sequenceDiagram
    participant L as Learner
    participant WA as Web Application
    participant VL as Voice Live API
    participant LLM as Azure OpenAI<br/>(GPT-4.1)
    participant AVT as TTS Avatar<br/>(DragonHD)

    Note over L,AVT: CONNECTION PHASE

    L->>WA: 1. Open app + Connect Avatar
    WA->>VL: 2. WebSocket → session.update<br/>{language, DragonHD voice, avatar}
    VL->>AVT: 3. session.update {modalities: [text,audio,avatar],<br/>voice, avatar, semantic VAD}
    AVT-->>VL: 4. session.updated {ICE servers}
    VL-->>WA: 5. Forward ICE servers
    WA->>AVT: 6. WebRTC handshake (SDP offer/answer)
    Note over WA,AVT: WebRTC connected

    Note over L,AVT: AVATAR PRESENTS SLIDE

    L->>WA: 7. Navigate to slide N
    WA->>LLM: 8. Translate speaker notes (if needed)
    LLM-->>WA: 9. Translated text
    WA->>VL: 10. conversation.item.create {text}
    WA->>VL: 11. response.create
    VL->>AVT: 12. TTS + Avatar render (DragonHD)
    AVT-->>L: 13. Video + audio stream (WebRTC)

    Note over L,AVT: Q&A MODE

    L->>WA: 14. Ask question about slide
    WA->>LLM: 15. generate_embedding(question)
    WA->>WA: 16. numpy cosine similarity (top 3)
    WA->>LLM: 17. RAG: generate answer with context
    LLM-->>WA: 18. Grounded answer
    WA-->>L: 19. Display answer + source slides
